{"id":948,"date":"2024-06-28T19:54:18","date_gmt":"2024-06-28T19:54:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/?p=948"},"modified":"2024-06-28T20:00:51","modified_gmt":"2024-06-28T20:00:51","slug":"donatie-rotary-club-paramaribo-quota","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/2024\/06\/28\/donatie-rotary-club-paramaribo-quota\/","title":{"rendered":"Donatie Rotary Club Paramaribo Quota"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Op 7 juni 2024, namen de voorzitter en penningmeester van Stichting Prasoro een symbolische cheque in ontvangst. De donatie is afkomstig van Rotary Club Paramaribo Quota. Deze donatie zal gebruikt worden voor de renovatie van de keuken in het tehuis. De werkzaamheden hiervan gaan halverwege juli van start . Wij zullen hierover ook updates geven.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-949\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Toespraak-Rotary-Quota-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Toespraak-Rotary-Quota-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Toespraak-Rotary-Quota-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-955\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Donatie-Rotary-Quota-2-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Donatie-Rotary-Quota-2-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Donatie-Rotary-Quota-2-1-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Op 7 juni 2024, namen de voorzitter en penningmeester van Stichting Prasoro een symbolische cheque in ontvangst. De donatie is afkomstig van Rotary Club Paramaribo Quota. Deze donatie zal gebruikt [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-948","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-uncategorized"],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/948","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=948"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/948\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":975,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/948\/revisions\/975"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=948"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=948"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=948"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}